<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n42027h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42027h">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42027h"> 27(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ &mdash; garment ~</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Perhaps Dr. Polding will inform me why I should, for so many years, and not only I, but very many members of my poor, deluded family, pay the priests for relics &mdash; such as &ldquo;the word of the cross,&rdquo; &ldquo;holy bones,&rdquo; &ldquo;holy wax,&rdquo; &ldquo;holy fire,&rdquo; &ldquo;pieces of saints&apos; garments&rdquo; from Rome and other places; &hellip; etc. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 143</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
